{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_013m7kmeuGTSNz3oUwy4SE9N","type":"tool_result","content":"  1165→**Step 3: Implement Curator**\n  1166→\n  1167→Create `internal/evolution/curator.go`:\n  1168→\n  1169→The Curator:\n  1170→1. Reads the current prompt file\n  1171→2. Sends it to the LLM with the lesson, asking it to merge the lesson as a\n  1172→   structured bullet/rule (ACE-style curation) while preserving existing content\n  1173→3. Creates a snapshot of the original file in `.cloche/evolution/snapshots/`\n  1174→4. Writes the LLM's response as the new file content\n  1175→5. Returns a `Change` record\n  1176→\n  1177→The LLM system prompt should instruct ACE-style curation: append as a structured\n  1178→bullet if new, update in place if it refines an existing rule, deduplicate.\n  1179→\n  1180→**Step 4: Run tests**\n  1181→\n  1182→Run: `go test ./internal/evolution/ -run TestCurator -v`\n  1183→Expected: ALL PASS\n  1184→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1dfc0695-6634-43c9-8fed-44daebf0ccee","uuid":"22336552-9b2a-41ef-b34c-1b4e4ddf6836","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspace/docs/plans/2026-02-24-self-evolution-implementation.md","content":"**Step 3: Implement Curator**\n\nCreate `internal/evolution/curator.go`:\n\nThe Curator:\n1. Reads the current prompt file\n2. Sends it to the LLM with the lesson, asking it to merge the lesson as a\n   structured bullet/rule (ACE-style curation) while preserving existing content\n3. Creates a snapshot of the original file in `.cloche/evolution/snapshots/`\n4. Writes the LLM's response as the new file content\n5. Returns a `Change` record\n\nThe LLM system prompt should instruct ACE-style curation: append as a structured\nbullet if new, update in place if it refines an existing rule, deduplicate.\n\n**Step 4: Run tests**\n\nRun: `go test ./internal/evolution/ -run TestCurator -v`\nExpected: ALL PASS\n","numLines":20,"startLine":1165,"totalLines":204